ont-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lTh2Bx8P5jQ\">Video of Trump Rally</a>, Right Side Broadcasting, &quot;Full Speech: Donald Trump Rally in Concord, NC (3-7-16)&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email interview with Hope Hicks, campaign spokeswoman for Donald Trump</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Public Policy Polling, <a href=\"http://www.publicpolicypolling.com/pdf/2011/PPP_Release_NC_815.pdf\">August 15, 2013 poll</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sporting News, &quot;<a href=\"http://www.sportingnews.com/nascar-news/4497934-brian-france-divorce-documents-salary-net-worth-homes-nascar-chairman-wife-megan\">Brian France divorce documents show net worth of NASCAR Chairman</a>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Motorsport, &quot;<a href=\"http://www.motorsport.com/nascar-cup/news/nascar-chief-brian-france-defends-trump-endorsement-to-employees-677132/\">NASCAR chief Brian France defends Trump endorsement to employees</a>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Charlotte Observer, &quot;<a href=\"http://www.charlotteobserver.com/sports/nascar-auto-racing/thatsracin/article63382092.html\">NASCAR CEO endorses Donald Trump 4 decades after grandfather endorsed George Wallace</a>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Associated Press, &quot;<a href=\"http://bigstory.ap.org/article/e466be0077ad4c2d9ebd6efee6918da0/nascar-distances-itself-donald-trump-after-remarks\">NASCAR distances itself from Donald Trump after remarks</a>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ESPN, &quot;<a href=\"http://espn.go.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/9488280/daytona-dynasty\">DAYTONA DYNASTY: An insider&#39;s up-close-and-personal chronicle of the France family, the most powerful lineage in American sports</a>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"widget widget_contact-us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-fam